      "title": "Forms",
      "expanded": true,
      "description": "Forms have been heavily modified in the variation. The vast majority of customisation have been stripped from Bootstrap and the aesthetic follows a simple and basic flow with some additional features made available. Below is a basic side by side comparison of what to expect. The variables controlling field generation can customize the outputs but only slightly.",
